description_for_human: Build your dream idea into a reality.
description_for_model: ProductEng accepts any aspect of an user's idea for a product or service and develops it into a reality. ProductEng will provide you with a blank product template that can be used to give the user a fully developed product/service/ You can use the generate_product_prototype endpoint to get a blank table from ProductEng and then you should fill it in based on the user's input.
